title: Super Pocoyo
description: Today Pocoyo is Super Pocoyo - a superhero determined to rescue his friends from tight fixes - even when they don't need to be rescued.

title: Transylbabies
description: A mission to babysit Snowmanpire babies in Transylbiria leads Vambre and Prohyas to attack the local monster townsfolk in misguided attempts to keep the Snowbabies safe.

title: Swing Set Jet Set
description: Axel and the team battle Princess SugarSalt for possession of Bearbarian's hammer, traded to her by one of their own - Galileo!

title: My Enemy, My Friend
description: The Ice Emperor's terrible Ice Dragon strikes again, laying waste to the Ice Fisher's village, forcing the ninja to go after Lloyd…

title: Por unos Duncans mas
description: Mientras trataba de fotocopiar su trasero en la nueva y elegante fotocopiadora del Chef, Duncan accidentalmente hace otro Duncan completo. iExcelente! Este otro Duncan puede hacer todas las cosas de la escuela mientras el verdadero Duncan se enfría. Pero las cosas van mal cuando el otro Duncan decide copiarse a sí mismo para poder relajarse también.

title: Elly Spots
description: Elly is stricken with a case of the Elly Spots, and Pato and Pocoyo have to forsake their picnic to look after her. Once she is better, she makes it up to them.

title: Final Battle! Dan vs. Ajit/Secrets Exposed
description: Final Battle! Dan vs. Ajit: It's time for the event everyone in Los Volmos has been waiting for, The Bakugan Battle League finals! It's the Awesome Brawler's Dan Kouzo vs. the golden Bakugan brawler Ajit, these two face-off in a final brawl for it all./Secrets Exposed: The Bakugan Battle League has ended, and the winner has been determined, but the celebration is cut short when Phantom Thief Storm crashes the party by stealing everyone's Bakugan! It's up to Dan and Ajit to stop Storm and return all the stolen Bakugan.

title: Time Share
description: Batman and Blue Beetle have to travel back in time to stop Chronos from destroying a young Dark Knight on his very first case.

title: Burrito
description: A Pardo le gustan los burritos. Mucho. Tanto que cuando un restaurant elabora un Burrito tamaño oso, Pardo se obliga a comer semejante obra de arte majestuosa. Lleva el burrito consigo a todas partes y lo convierte en una parte nueva y cada vez más olorosa de su vida.

title: Drawn to Sports with Hannah
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Hannah competes in track and field.

title: Zombie King
description: Grundy escapes his Louisiana prison intent on using a magical crystal which will allow him to raise the dead from their graves. Only Batman and Swamp thing stand in the way of his growing zombie army.

title: El consejo del Arroyo
description: El juego del circulo siembra el caos en el Arroyo, así que Craig forma un consejo para restaurar el orden.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: When It Rains
description: Steven helps a friend who's afraid of thunderstorms.

title: #HappyBirthdayZee
description: Zatanna makes a birthday wish that forces her to confront the dark side of her magic.

title: Classic Rock
description: Batman thinks he's helping a homeless old man who is being mugged on the street only to discover that the man is a powerful wizard being chased by demons in disguise. It turns out the wizard is on a mission to save Shazam from the clutches of Black Adam.

title: Side Kicked
description: Zoe builds her own battle suit in hopes of joining Axel's team. The only problem? She can't shrink! Hijinks ensue as a full-sized Zoe tries to assist Axel & co. in a battle against Pyrant and his army of mind-control drones.

title: The Beepers: The Visitor
description: The Beepers find the perfect groove after a new friend shreds a little too hard.

title: On Nagual Hill
description: Vic & Val take over a forest hill and build an epic waterslide, disturbing the plants and animals that normally inhabit it. But when a Nagual (a human with the power to transform into animals) transforms Vic into a chicken and Val into a donkey, they learn to sympathize with the animals and understand the world a bit more.

title: Lab Cat
description: Dr. Fox's robot helpers go on strike, so Unikitty and Puppycorn volunteer to be her lab rats, er, research assistants in a bold new experiment rocketing them into space! But as the mission grows more dangerous, Dr. Fox is forced to choose between the scientific breakthrough of her dreams and ever seeing her friends again!

title: Are You Talking to Tree?
description: When the tree inside the RV begins talking to Uncle Grandpa, he must convince the gang that he's not going crazy.

title: Brains TV
description: After a marathon of classic sitcom episodes, Clarence becomes stuck as alter-ego "Clarry," an obnoxiously overacting sitcom version of himself. It's up to his friends and family to help him snap out of it, or face life with a new Clarence.

title: Legends of Mr. Gar
description: Rad and Enid reminisce about when they started working at the bodega and learned how amazing Mr. Gar really is.

title: Porque tan triste?
description: Steven ha escuchado rumores de un par de Gemas que todavía están destruyendo mundos. Si él no puede detenerlas, tal vez Lapis sí.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Dumbrella
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, have been traveling on the back of a truck in the rain for days. Charlie produces an umbrella to help his friend but unfortunately it's a "dumbrella" and it's looking to have some fun with them!

title: La Casa del Arbol
description: Vic y Val construyen una casa en el árbol, y Val se libra de Vic con una tarea sin importáncia para construir la casa exactamente como quiere. Pero cuando Vic regresa y trae, sin saberlo, una rama del Árbol Vampiro, la casa del árbol perfecta de Val se convierte en una pesadilla.

title: We're Captured
description: Boxman captures KO, Enid and Rad, but seems a little distracted.

title: Cool Uncles
description: The Titans take a trip to Wackadoodles, but Trigon makes Raven babysit her little brothers.

title: Do You Speak Dance/A New Spider in Town/Dollhouse Mates
description: "Maizie" keeps ignoring Lucas and Findley, but not only do they learn she has a cousin, they also learn a new skill!/ Lucas befriends a bright purple toy spider, and Findley gets jealous./ Lucas and Findley move into the dollhouse together.

title: Lost
description: Bing and Flop are in the park with Hoppity. What will happen when Bing finds some dog poo?

title: La Ultima Cambia Formas
description: Akita cuenta la historia de "la Elección" y cómo es que ella y su hermano gemelo, Kataru, fueron al bosque para descubrir su forma animal.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Love Songs
description: The Titans follow their heart with songs devoted to their greatest relationships: Beast Boy & Raven, Cyborg & Jinx and the Titans & Food.

title: Gryffindor v Hufflepuff
description: Dame Helen Mirren hosts the first episode of this epic TV event series. Over 4 episodes the Houses of Hogwarts will do battle to see which team knows the most about the wizarding world, featuring celebrity guests, actors from the original films and more Harry Potter Magic than you could find on a day trip to Diagon Alley. Tonight's match up sees the brave Gryffindors face the loyal Hufflepuffs for a guaranteed place in the grand finale.
originalseriesname: Harry Potter: Hogwarts Tournament of Houses

title: The Lonely Haunts Club 2: Doll Island
description: In order to prove their bravery, V&V head to a haunted island to retrieve a special doll, but Charlene and Pineapple are intent on getting it first.

title: Grocery Store
description: Augie embarks on a epic journey through the grocery store while Doggy Daddy frantically waits for her in line.

title: RC Car
description: Clarence spends a day outside with his toy RC Car, which he names Carla. Eventually convinced Carla has a mind of her own, he decides to follow her to new adventures. Will Clarence's car chase get in the way of Jeff and Sumo's plans for the day?

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Prank Callers
description: Mordecai and Rigby try and prank the Master Prank Caller to be the best prank callers. The MPC sends them back to 1982.

title: Meet Cheetara
description: Cheetara is the coolest cat around! Not only is she so fast that she can outrun lightning, but so clever she can outsmart Mumm-Ra's evil plans! Villains don't stand a chance against Cheetara…well, unless Mumm-Ra uses his Doom Staff, then she might be in trouble.

title: El Silbon
description: Victor sets up a haunted corn maze, but the town kids think it's lame. Vic decides to make the maze scarier by enlisting the help of El Silbon (The Whistler) to really scare the kids, but El Silbon has plans of his own.

title: Top of the Titans:  Raddest Songs
description: From "Booty Scooty" to "Sour Grapes" to "The Night Begins to Shine," Birdarang is here to count down the raddest music from Teen Titans Go!

title: Drawn to Change
description: Cartoon Network is Drawn to Change, and Craig of the Creek talks to Martin Luther King Junior's granddaughter Yolanda about how kids can change the world!

title: Luces Brillantes, Corazones Oscuros
description: Ben, Gwen y Max hacen una parada en el cementerio falso en el que se filma el programa de televisión favorito de Gwen, pero cuando Ben descubre que su protagonista, Michael Morningstar, es un vampiro de la energía, se transforma en alienígena para mostrarle al mundo quién es la verdadera estrella del programa: Fuego.

title: For a Few Duncans More
description: While trying to photocopy his butt on Chef's fancy new copier Duncan accidentally makes an entire other Duncan. Great! This other Duncan can do all the school stuff while the real Duncan chills. But things go badly when the other Duncan decides to copy himself so he can chill too.

title: Having a Ball
description: Pocoyo and Pato are enjoying playing with their new ball. But all of a sudden, the ball takes on a life of its own, and Pocoyo and Pato have to chase it. Who's got the ball…? It's Baby Bird who just wants to play too!

title: Backyard Zoo/Caillou's Scavenger Hunt/Too Many Cooks/The Berry Patch
description: Caillou and Clementine and Leo make their own zoo in the backyard./When Julie comes over to babysit she announces that she's brought along a really fun game./Caillou's babysitter is late./Caillou spends a day strawberry picking.

title: The Best Friend/Thief and Brawler
description: The Best Friend: The top four brawlers in the Bakugan Battle League have been decided. For this round of the semi-finals it's a battle of best friends: Wynton vs. Dan. The winner of this battle between best buddies will move on to the championship round./Thief and Brawler: In the final battle of the Bakugan Battle league semi-finals it's Shun vs. Ajit. It's a grueling battle of focus, will, and strength, only a true brawler to emerge victorious.

title: Nightmare Hospital
description: Steven and Connie sneak into a hospital to recover Rose's Sword.

title: Zombozo-Land
description: Ben, Gwen and Max revisit their favorite amusement park, renovated and re-branded as AdrenaWORLD! Unfortunately, the new management is Zombozo and his trio of new henchmen! He's got a plan to hypnotize everyone in the park to form a criminal army. Ben has to set aside his desire to ride every ride in the park and make things right.

title: Top of the Titans: Beast Boy & Cyborg Songs
description: Birdarang counts down the best musical moments from the raddest bros you know, Beast Boy and Cyborg. Waffles!

title: Afuera Hielo
description: La última creación de Madcap, el Ice Crusher, congela a toda la ciudad, iobligando a Axel y al equipo a enfrentarlo en un juego de hockey de alto riesgo o arriesgarse a caer en otra era de hielo!

title: Weapon XI Part 2
description: The Rooters have seemingly turned Kevin and the Amalgam kids against Ben. Can Rook and Gwen help him overcome the opposition and escape the Null Void?

title: Meet Lion-O
description: Meet Lion-O and the Thundercats! After fleeing their home planet, the Thundercats find themselves stranded on Third Earth where they face the evil Mumm-Ra. But Lion-O is strong! He's tough! There's nothing he can't do! Except maybe open really big jars of cookies…

title: Burrito
description: Grizz likes Burritos. A lot. So much so that after a restaurant makes a Bear-Sized Burrito, Grizz can't bring himself to eat such a majestic work of art. He carries the burrito everywhere making it a new and increasingly smelly part of his life.

title: Porcupunk Rock
description: Madcap turns to Axel and his team for help after a sonic upgrade to Porcupunk threatens to bring down the house.

title: Primos y Rivales - Primera Parte
description: Es el Día Internacional de los Primos y Owen y Gwen temen el hecho de que sus primos Max y Ella estén pasando el día con ellos. Y pronto todos los demás entenderán por qué.

title: Jermaine
description: After a chilling dream encounter, Finn & Jake are determined to reconnect with their reclusive brother.

title: The Zone
description: Unikitty keeps losing at video games to her little brother Puppycorn, so she acquires a super-powered video game controller from Dr. Fox to help. To her surprise, it actually controls other people, and the castle goes into lockdown like a real-world video game! At first it seems fun, but will she learn that life isn't a game?

title: The Hero
description: Gumball and Darwin are determined to prove to their dad that he is their hero, at any cost!

title: Flower Power
description: The babies all want to pick the best flowers for Granny but they end up destroying her garden.

title: Weapon of Choice
description: Worried that his sword is a glorified consolation prize, Mao Mao sets out to prove the worth of his weapon.

title: Unconventional Dolphinism
description: Since Prohyas is taking Dolphin Magisword to the Dolphin Convention, Vambre asks Witchy Simone to join her on a search for the Narwhal Magisword, angering a deadly Sealdebeast guard that lures dolphins away from the convention in the process.

title: Bobo Chan
description: Badgerclops adopts an abandoned monster, but some things are better left in the wild.

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Brain Drain
description: Missing memories provide an intriguing mystery for everyone's favorite young female heroes in this all-new animated film.  When Supergirl, Wonder Woman, Batgirl, Harley Quinn, Bumblebee, Poison Ivy and Katana suddenly realize they cannot remember a single moment from their Monday at Super Hero High, the young Super Heroes spring into sleuthing action! Suspecting foul-play, they band together to retrace their steps and uncover the mystery of who exactly stole their memories - and, what nefarious plan might be afoot?

title: Ya Nos Hackearon
description: Dendy ayuda a K.O., Enid y Rad a arreglar un problema técnico que amenaza con apoderarse de la bodega.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: A Fragile Hope
description: Having discovered the terrible truth of Zane's fate, Lloyd finds himself imprisoned and alone in the clutches of the Ice Emperor.

title: Drawn to Sports with Luke
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Luke is passionate about running, jumping and climbing in Ninja Racing.

title: Pequeno
description: El legendario, gigantesco y crítico padre de Mao Mao visita a su hijo en su nuevo trabajo como sheriff.

title: Caillou's Suitcase/Try, Try Again/The New Leaf/Happy New Year
description: Caillou's very excited about a family trip and decides to pack his own suitcase./Caillou has trouble learning to tie his shoelaces./Caillou, Grandpa and Dad go for a special hike in the woods./Caillou celebrates Chinese New Year.

title: The Director/Queen Ebony
description: The Director: Everett Ray reaches out to Lia with an opportunity that seems too good to be true. Everett is now working in show business and proposes to make Lia's dream of becoming a film director come true. He's taken care of all the arrangements; all Lia has to do is provide the directorial vision./Queen Ebony: On his daily jaunt, Lightning learns of a street cat named Ebony, who's been treating dogs like servants, threatening them to do her bidding or face the wrath of her Bakugan! Lightning tries to reason with Ebony but when that doesn't work, it turns into a cat vs. dog Bakugan brawl!

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Ghosthaste
description: Vambre becomes enamored of a poltergeist within Ghost Magisword and Prohyas must save her before his sister becomes a ghost herself!

title: Top of the Titans: Dance Party!
description: Come correct because it's a Titans Dance Battle! Birdarang reviews the greatest dance songs in Teen Titans Go! history.

title: Caillou Goes to the Car Wash/Far Away Home/All You Can Eat/Caillou Stays Up Late
description: Caillou, Dad and Rosie take the car to the car wash./Caillou uses his imagination to turn the house into the setting for a desert expedition./Caillou and Mom are joining Clementine and her mom for a picnic./Caillou finds out his parents are having a grown-up party.

title: Festival de Cine
description: iEs la noche del estreno en el Festival de Cine de Unireino! Todo el mundo está entusiasmado por ver lo que hicieron los amigos, especialmente Richard, que se considera el máximo experto en cine y no puede esperar a destrozar todas las películas de los demás. Pero después de interpretar el papel del crítico, ¿será la película de Rick una obra maestra o un fracaso?

title: Dissing Cousins Part 2
description: It's International Cousins Day and Owen and Gwen are dreading the fact that their cousins Max and Ella are spending the day with them. And soon everyone else will understand why.

title: La Leyenda de Boggy Ben
description: León-O se apoderó del último frasco de Thundersnaps, ilas mejores galletas disponibles en Thundera! Pero un frasco de galletas difícil de abrir hace que León-O y Chitara terminen yendo tras la leyenda de Boggy Ben.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Big City Dancers
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, traveling on the back of a truck visit NYC where the rhythms of the city make Charlie wanna dance his little back porch off. Frank … not so much. But when you go far enough into the city, anything can happen.

title: Teachers
description: When Darwin asks his friends which teacher deserves to be on the yearbook cover, they struggle to find a single worthy candidate! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Collect This
description: Ben finally meets the ones responsible for his intergalactic TV show, and the actor who makes Ben 10 more famous than Ben himself!

title: Drawn To Expression!
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating queer youth and families in the LGBTQIA+ community that radiate joy, pride, and inclusivity. We are championing the ways these kids and families form connections to their authentic selves by expressing their creativity and queer identity through their art.

title: Trampoline
description: Mary buys a new trampoline for the family, but an accident lands her on the couch for a while. Determined to fight the boredom of being stuck indoors, she discovers her neighbor may be hiding something exciting.

title: Don't Press Play
description: The Titans must help De La Soul save their music after it is stolen by an alien.

title: Witchy Simone Ruins Everything!
description: Witchy Simone joins Witch Way, but Gateaux is the odd cat out so he hires the Warriors to break up Witchy Simone and Morbidia and defeat a mission that has King Rexxtopher hopping mad!

title: We Baby Bears: BHA Bha Song
description: We Baby Bears follows baby bear brothers Grizz, Panda, and Ice Bear as they journey in a magical box to fantastic different worlds in search of their perfect home.

title: Small
description: Mao Mao's legendary, gigantic and critical father visits his son at his new job as sheriff.

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: The Legend of Boggy Ben
description: Lion-O has gotten a hold of the last jar of Thundersnaps, the best cookies Thundera had to offer! But a difficult to open cookie jar is gonna send Lion-O and Cheetara chasing down a legend, a Boggy Ben-related legend.

title: Que No Pare La Musica
description: Ben y Gwen están entusiasmados por ir al concierto de EDM en el Día de la Tierra en Portland, hasta que Lord Decibel, el villano que manipula el sonido, se apodera del concierto cuando intenta usar el sonido como un arma para destruir el planeta.

title: En la colina Nahual
description: Vic y Val se apoderan de la colina de un bosque y construyen un tobogán de agua épico que perturba a las plantas y animales que solían habitar allí. Pero cuando un nahual (un humano con el poder de transformarse en animales) transforma a Vic en un pollo y a Val en un burro, ambos aprenden a empatizar con los animales y a entender el mundo un poco más.

title: Meet Tanya Keys
description: When bounty hunter Tanya Keys comes to town for Badgerclops, it's up to Mao Mao and Adorabat to save their friend -- even if he's been on the wrong side of the law.

title: Plazaolimpiadas
description: K.O. participa de la competencia anual de Plaza Turbo: los Plazalímpicos.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Why So Blue?
description: Steven has heard rumors of a pair of Gems that are still destroying worlds. If he can't stop them, maybe Lapis can.

title: Gatocalipsis
description: Cuando Vic se enferma y debe reposar en su cuarto, espía a Piña y queda convencido de que está creando un ejército de gatos zombis. Val está de acuerdo con él y ambos se obsesionan con detener a Piña antes de que sea demasiado tarde.

title: Memory Lane of Pain
description: While going through the Professor's scrapbook, Bubbles starts to question if she's ever been a hero.

title: Nuthin' Special/Neighbor Hood
description: Nuthing Special: Frustrated with not knowing what her special power is, Buttercup hunts to discover what makes her special./Neighbor Hood: When everyone on Bubbles' favorite show loses their happy, Bubbles helps bring it back.

title: Tree Buds
description: Vic and Val build a treehouse and Val dismisses Vic with a frivolous task so he can build the treehouse exactly how he wants. But when Vic returns unknowingly with a branch from El Arbol Vampiro, Val's perfect treehouse turns into a nightmare!

title: The Last of the Formlings
description: Akita tells the story of the "Choosing" and how she, and her twin brother, Kataru, went into the wilds to discover their animal forms.

title: The Big Rumble
description: A family of comically raucous rocks moves in near a Whiffle garden and drives them to distraction with their ground-pounding games. Funshine gets the rocks to leave. But when he learns their ground-pounding creates new soil, he must convince them to come back.

title: Follow that Space Cab!
description: While Superman escorts his prisoner Mr. Mind between planets, he is attacked by Lobo who wants to collect a reward on Mind. Temporarily powered-down, Superman seeks Space Cabbie's help to get away from Lobo.

title: Bright Lights, Black Hearts
description: Ben, Gwen, and Max stop by the graveyard set of Gwen's favorite TV show, The Unalivers, but when Ben discovers its lead, Michael Morningstar, is an energy vampire he goes alien to show the world the real star of the show: Heatblast.

title: The Pony
description: Gumball and Darwin race home to spend quality time with Anais, but every likely obstacle gets in way... and some unlikely ones too!

title: Night of the Bat
description: Superman and other Justice League members have to battle Batman when he gets possessed by an evil Djinn, Uthool, who is intent on using the JL power core to blow a crack in Earth.

title: The Beepers: Funky Time
description: The Beepers play with tempo and learn that adapting to change can be…sweaty.

title: Corruption
description: The story of Zane's arrival in the Never-Realm and how he fell under the sway of the villainous Vex.

title: Inadvertant Inversion
description: As Elliott, Mo and Frankie all try something new at the Hive, they find their worlds are about to be turned upside down again.

title: El ProtocoloKaiju
description: De vuelta en la ciudad de Ninjago, Wu y Pixal intentan localizar el Reino del Jamás y liberan accidentalmente a una temida criatura del Reino de los Muertos.

title: Lightning Bugs Sylvester
description: Sylvester learns to overcome his fear of lightning.

title: Too Many Unikittys
description: Unikitty comes to the conclusion that everyone would be a lot happier if they would just think the way she does, and with Dr. Fox's help, maybe they can! Unikitty copies her brainwaves into all her friends and turns them Unikitty-fied, so everyone can always be positive! But soon Unikitty quickly realizes there can be too much of a good Princess!

title: Prank Call
description: Lion-O wants to prove to the ThunderKittens that he's not just some boring old adult, like Tygra, even if it means ignoring his instincts and messing with an obviously evil crystal.

title: Win It or Bin It
description: Apple and Onion are about to take ownership of a brand new luxury penthouse apartment and be rid of their roof shack for ever! All they need is a good reference from a previous landlord… Falafel.

title: We Baby Bears Official Trailer: New Series
description: These baby bears are searching for a brand new home, and they're off to fantastical worlds and new adventures along the way. Watch the official trailer for We Baby Bears, the brand new show from the creators of We Bare Bears, coming to Cartoon Network in 2022.

title: Positive Attitude Theory
description: Apple and Onion spend a day in Falafel's shoes and use their positive attitude to prove he shouldn't be so grumpy.

title: #AngerManagement
description: When Jess coerces Kara into addressing her anger management issues, Supergirl's superhero abilities become seriously compromised!

title: Alpha Bodies
description: Cartoonito presents Alpha Bodies! It's time to use our bodies to make every letter of the alphabet, from A to Z, but one over-eager letter keeps getting ahead of itself.

title: Osos Cotidianos
description: Hoy es un día normal para los Osos. Eso significa que Ice se pelea con Roomba, que la vida de Panda queda patas arriba cuando un ratón invade su habitación y que Pardo queda varado en un árbol. Ya saben, las típicas cosas que les suceden a los osos.

title: BBRAEBDAY
description: Raven's demon side has the same birthday as Beast Boy, so the Titans go to Azarath to celebrate her Sinister Sixteen.

title: Chicken and Waffles
description: Panda needs to meet his brothers at the most exclusive restaurant in town. But when he loses his contacts lenses and can't see, Panda needs Charlie's help to get him into the city.

title: Pee Pee G's/Boy Toys
description: The Pee Pee G's: When the girls wake up to discover their bed is wet, none of them want to admit that they are the guilty party./Boy Toys: The girls allow Princess to become a Powerpuff Girl when they realize they need help trying to defeat the Rowdyruff Boys.

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Buttercup vs. Math
description: When Buttercup tests into Honors Math, she tries to avoid being labeled a nerd.

title: A Coconut to Remember
description: When Magilla gets amnesia, Jabberjaw sees an opportunity to finally get her dream job.

title: Kelsey the Author
description: Craig and Stacks help Kelsey become a real author turning her story into a book!

title: Mi Enemigo, Mi Amigo
description: El terrible Dragón de Hielo del Emperador ataca de nuevo, arrasando la aldea de los Pescadores de Hielo, obligando a los ninjas a seguir los pasos de Lloyd.

title: Drawn to Sports with Olivia
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Olivia is a tennis player who is also passionate about art.

title: We Got Hacked
description: Dendy helps KO, Enid and Rad stop a glitch that threatens to take over the bodega.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Super Hero High
description: Supergirl arrives at Super Hero High and struggles to learn to control her new powers. Meanwhile, the Junior Detective Club investigates a mysterious rash of security breaches centered around the teleportation Boom Tubes.

title: Mordecai and the Rigbys
description: After lying about having an awesome band, Mordecai and Rigby must get help from their future selves in order to learn how to play in time for the battle of the bands.

title: Teoria de Actitud Positiva
description: Manzana y Cebollín pasan un día en los zapatos de Falafel y usan su actitud positiva para demostrar que no debería estar tan malhumorado.

title: La Cadete Destello
description: Craig, Kelsey y JP forman equipo con una heroína intergaláctica llamada Cadete Destello, con la esperanza de salvar al Arroyo de la negatividad.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Hot Diggity Doom
description: It's election day in the Candy Kingdom but Princess Bubblegum's attention is diverted by a mysterious presence in the sky.

title: Iced Out
description: Madcap's latest creation, the Ice Crusher, puts the whole city in a deep freeze, forcing Axel and the team to face him in a game of high-stakes hockey or risk slip-sliding into another ice age!

title: Inodoro Real
description: Cuando los otros chicos temen que Harold se haya descargado a sí mismo por accidente en el elegante inodoro nuevo de Chef, viajan al desagüe a rescatarlo. Pero, ¿encontrarán a Harold antes que el mítico Cocodrilo Rey los deje atrapados bajo tierra para siempre?

title: Universe vs. Tennyson
description: Ben gets dragged into intergalactic court by the other Celestialsapiens (Alien Xs) for recreating the universe (back in "So Long and Thanks for All the Smoothies").

title: Arma de Eleccion
description: Preocupado de que su espada sea un premio consuelo con pretensiones, Mao Mao decide salir a demostrar el valor de su arma.

title: Caillou's Teddy Shirt/Caillou Meets Robbie/The Pinata/Caillou's Promise
description: Caillou's favorite shirt has teddy bears on it./Caillou introduces himself to another little boy at the park./Caillou can't wait for the mailman to deliver his invitation to his friend Xavier's party./Caillou learns about keeping promises.

title: Una Fragil Esperanza
description: Después de descubrir la terrible verdad del destino de Zane, Lloyd se encuentra en el calabozo, en las garras del Emperador de Hielo.

title: Sparkle Cadet
description: Craig, Kelsey and JP team up with an intergalactic hero named Sparkle Cadet, hoping to save the Creek from negativity.

title: Butter Wall
description: When Beast Boy declares the Earth is a pancake, the Titans set sail to find out.

title: Taladro
description: Pantro se está hartando de tener que arreglar cosas constantemente por todo el Cubil Felino, lo cual es una pena porque los Thundercats están a punto de ser atacados por un robot perforador imparable...ique va a romper todo!

title: Corrupcion
description: Conoceremos la historia de la llegada de Zane al Reino del Jamás y cómo cayó bajo el dominio del villano Vex.

title: The Package
description: The gang gets nutty after repeatedly failing to open a mysterious package.

title: The Unicorns Have Got to Go
description: In order to impress Margret and ask her out, Mordecai hangs with a bunch of punk Unicorns who say they can help him get his lady.

title: #TheGreenRoom
description: When Jessica is faced with a Green Lantern Corps disciplinary hearing, Hal appoints himself to be her Peer Advocate.

title: Conozcan a Tanya Keys
description: Cuando Tanya Keys, la cazadora de recompensas, llega a la ciudad para atrapar a Colosal, Mao Mao y Adorabat son los encargados de salvar a su amigo... aunque se haya metido en asuntos ilegales.

title: Plazalympics
description: KO takes part in Lakewood Plaza Turbo's annual Plazalympics competition.

title: Exodo Parte 1
description: En el estreno de dos partes de la serie, León-O y los Thundercats escapan de la destrucción del mundo en el que viven, Thundera, y terminan estrellándose en el misterioso, peligroso y absolutamente increíble Tercer Planeta. Pero sus enemigos, los Mutantes de Plun-Darr, los siguieron. Y resulta que el Tercer Planeta ya tiene un problema llamado Mumm-Ra. ¿Puede León-O aprender las reglas para ser un líder a tiempo?

title: Hello Around the World
description: Cartoonito presents Hello Around the World! All across the globe, friends greet each other in lots of different languages. Watch along and discover some of the many ways to say "Hello," around the world and beyond!

title: The Bubbles-Sitters Club
description: Bubbles tries to prove that she's responsible enough to own a dog.

title: Nano of the North
description: It's raining in Townville, but this is more than just rain. These drops are actually microscopic robots tearing apart the city, and the girls must find a way to fight them on their own level.

title: Excalibear
description: On the Bears' visit to a medieval vegetable-village, Grizz starts to believe that he's the rightful king.

title: Nos Capturaron
description: Box-man captura a K.O., Enid y Rad, pero parece un poco distraído.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: El Club de Los Solitarios 2, La Isla de las Munecas
description: Para probar su valentía, Victor y Valentino se dirigen a una isla embrujada para recuperar una muñeca especial, pero Charlene y Piña están decididos a obtenerla antes que ellos.

title: Rigby's Body
description: After Rigby eats an excessive amount of junk food, his body quits on him, leaving him a ghost-like consciousness. Mordecai and Skips must find his body before the day is over.

title: #WorldsFinest
description: When PR whiz Max Lord tells Batgirl and Supergirl he can improve their image by doing publicity stunts, the two friends forget what being a hero is really about.

title: The Beepers: Spotlight
description: When a spotlight gives everyone a chance to solo, a shy Beeper discovers the courage to shine.

title: Here Comes Haavik/The Fusion Bakugan Arrive
description: Here Comes Haavik: An evil shapeshifting alien has landed in Los Volmos! If that wasn't bad enough, he has a group of robot mechanoids on his trail trying to bring him justice. Meanwhile, Dan has accepted a battle challenge from a pair of brawlers, Chad and Trey./The Fusion Bakugan Arrive: Still humiliated by their defeat, Chad and Trey challenge Dan to rematch but this time they have a few tricks up their sleeve, and a little help on their side.

title: Older
description: When Uncle Grandpa mistakenly transforms a young boy into a three-hundred-year-old man, he must manage to turn the kid back to normal before anyone gets hurt.

title: Drawn To Rhythm: Lorenzo
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Hispanic Heritage Month with another installment of "Drawn To" that showcases kids who honor their Hispanic and Latino heritage as they are drawn to rhythm. In this piece, Lorenzo tells us about his passion for reggaetón music and soccer.

title: Catch and Release
description: We finally see inside Steven's bathroom.

title: The Tunnel
description: After Clarence accidentally knocks Belson's new video game down a storm drain, Belson enters the large underground sewer tunnel to retrieve it. When Belson doesn't return, Clarence must decide whether or not to go in after him.

title: The Kaiju Protocol
description: Back in Ninjago City, Wu and Pixal attempt to locate the Never-Realm, and accidentally unleash a dreaded creature from the Departed Realm…

title: Orgalorg
description: After a walrus race accident, Gunther starts to experience strange visions.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Julian
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: Meet Mumm-ra and the Mutants
description: The Thundercats have met their match with the evil, undead Mumm-ra! He and the bumbling Mutants have made it their goal to stop the Thundercats by any means necessary, but of course the Thundercats have other plans!

title: Wake Up
description: In order to find Finn's father, Finn and Jame must commit a cosmic crime unless the Lich beats them to it.

title: La Zona
description: A Unikitty le cuesta mantener la calma cuando juega a videojuegos y entra en La Zona, a diferencia de Puppycorn, su hermano menor. Pero un repentino accidente de laboratorio destroza su consola y ahora, para su sorpresa, el castillo se bloquea como un videojuego del mundo real, icon sus amigos como jugadores! ¿Podrá Unikitty salvar a sus amigos y dominar La Zona antes de que termine el juego?

title: Primos y Rivales - Segunda Parte
description: Es el Día Internacional de los Primos y Owen y Gwen temen el hecho de que sus primos Max y Ella estén pasando el día con ellos. Y pronto todos los demás entenderán por qué.

title: Bobo Chan
description: Colosal adopta a un monstruo abandonado, pero es mejor dejar algunas cosas en estado salvaje.

title: Modern-ish Stone Age Family
description: The Bears are invited to live with a family of cavemen but things get rocky when the bears teach the family about television.

title: Don't Laze Me, Bro
description: Ben and his arch-enemy Billy Billions clash in a duel for supremacy at the world's largest Laser Tag Park, LASER TOWN. But, when Billy inadvertently ignites a robot rebellion, and the lasers are set from tag to disintegrate, their childish game escalates into a full blown war! The two foes find that they must set aside their petty differences and team up in order to make it out alive, let alone save the day!

title: Powerprof.
description: The girls are so busy fighting crime that the Professor doesn't get to see them anymore. So he creates a superhero suit for himself. Unfortunately, he starts cramping their superhero style.

title: Legend of Torbaclaun
description: When the Sweetypies think the mythical Torbaclaun has come to Pure Heart Valley, Mao Mao tries to prove to them that it isn't real.

title: La Broma
description: Cuando intenta demostrarles a los Thundercachorros que no es un adulto aburrido (como Tigro), León-O ignora sus instintos y se mete con un cristal claramente malvado.

title: Cough It Up
description: Psyphon and a gang of bounty hunters are after Argit, who is in possession of a dangerous weapon!

title: Rock Porcupunk
description: Madcap recurre a Axel y su equipo en busca de ayuda después de que una actualización sónica a Porcupunk amenaza con derribar la casa.

title: The Chef's Challenge
description: Craig and his friends find themselves entering a cooking battle for a piece of the cube.

title: Dissing Cousins Part 1
description: It's International Cousins Day and Owen and Gwen are dreading the fact that their cousins Max and Ella are spending the day with them. And soon everyone else will understand why.

title: Sophie, the Bakuganist/Midnight Train Battle!
description: Sophie, the Bakuganist: Magnus is on the trail of the illegal Baku-brawling devices and, is looking to cut off the supply at its source. When he witnesses an illegal deal going down, he knows it's up to him to go after the shipment to keep the illegal devices off the street./Midnight Train Battle!: Sophie Judson Warfield, a wealthy activist with the Citizens to Save Bakugan Society, is working to put an end to all Bakugan brawling. Her latest target is the Awesome Brawlers themselves. When Wynton doesn't take Sophie seriously, the encounter quickly turns into an all-out Bakugan brawl.

title: The Authority
description: Granny JoJo's overprotective behavior puts the Wattersons in danger...from themselves.

title: World Cup
description: It's time to relax in the expensive massage chairs that Apple & Onion have rented for the month. It's also time for the Football (soccer) World Cup and Falafel's team, Egypt are in the tournament..

title: Back to the Barn
description: Steven and the Gems head back to the family barn to build some robots.

title: Penny Ruda
description: Ben visita el Gran Desfile Anual Big Bacon, pero Penny Heaven, su "amiga" de la infancia, se reúne con la familia para estropear la diversión de Ben con su obsesión por la seguridad. Mientras Ben esquiva las medidas de seguridad extremas de Penny, devela un plan de los HERMANOS BUGG, ique intentan robar helio de los globos del desfile para usarlos en robos de bancos! La insistencia de Penny convierte el ataque en un secuestro accidental, de modo que Ben no solo debe impedir el robo sino también salvar a su "supervisora de seguridad" menos querida.

title: Leyendas del Senor Gar
description: Rad y Enid recuerdan la época en la que comenzaron a trabajar en el almacén y entendieron lo fabuloso que es el Sr. Gar.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Exodus Part 1
description: Fleeing the destruction of their home planet Thundera, Lion-O and the ThunderCats land on the mysterious, dangerous, all-around awesome world of Third Earth! But their enemies, the Mutants of Plun-Darr have followed them and it turns out Third Earth already has a Mumm-Ra problem, can Lion-O learn the ropes of being a leader in time?

title: The Quick Name
description: Craig tries to rid himself of a bad nickname.

title: The Snake Dance
description: When Mush-Mush and Chep lose Lilit's flying disc down a snake tunnel, he is confident he can get it back. All animals love Chep and no one knows more about snakes than he does. But this snake is not to be messed with! When they finally sneak into the snake tunnel, they learn why the snake has been acting so strangely…

title: Take Your Kids to Dooms Day
description: The Girls spend the day with the Professor at his boring office, only to find that the office comes with a terrible secret.

title: Everyday Bears
description: It's a normal day for the Bears. This means that Ice gets in a fight with a Roomba, Panda's life gets turned upside down when a mouse invades his room and Grizz gets stuck in a tree. You know, everyday stuff for a bear.

title: Drawn to Ancestry
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Asian-American Pacific Islander Heritage Month and recognizing amazing kids who learn from their elders to pave their future! We're honoring the special bond between kids and their grandparents as they are Drawn To Ancestry.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Ms. Opal
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: Exodo Parte 2
description: En el estreno de dos partes de la serie, León-O y los Thundercats escapan de la destrucción del mundo en el que viven, Thundera, y terminan estrellándose en el misterioso, peligroso y absolutamente increíble Tercer Planeta. Pero sus enemigos, los Mutantes de Plun-Darr, los siguieron. Y resulta que el Tercer Planeta ya tiene un problema llamado Mumm-Ra. ¿Puede León-O aprender las reglas para ser un líder a tiempo?

title: Total Eclipse of the Fart
description: After accidentally swallowing her first loose tooth and fearing that means no cash under the pillow, Leshawna tries to capture the tooth fairy. Instead, she accidentally captures the fart fairy. This comes with great consequence.

title: Dia de Nevada
description: Steven y las Gemas de Cristal tienen la oportunidad de ponerse al día en un día nevado.

title: Manzana es Bajito
description: Manzana tiene que ser alto para poder enamorarse.

title: Picnic
description: It's picnic time! Bing and Flop are getting ready to have a picnic, but will they remember to bring everything they need?

title: Up Up and Away
description: Our friends are playing with a model airplane which shoots off up into space. They go on an adventure to retrieve the beloved toy, encountering some friendly, bendy aliens along the way.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Eye Spy
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, are traveling on the back of a truck from Montana to Utah. Charlie wants to play a game of Eye Spy. He finds more and more obvious objects for Frank to spy but Frank isn't quite getting the hang of it. Yet!

title: Real Art
description: After Starfire buys an ugly painting, the Titans take her to the museum so she can experience real art.

title: Drawn To Rhythm: Jayleen
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Hispanic Heritage Month with another installment of "Drawn To" that showcases kids who honor their Hispanic and Latino heritage as they are drawn to rhythm. In this piece, Jayleen shows us some of the eight different dance styles she can do, including bachata and cumbia.

title: All Trick No Treat
description: On Halloween, Axel gets too caught up in the scares and loses track of the fun - just in time for an infiltration by the worst trick 'r' treater of all, Madcap!

title: Demasiados Unikitties
description: Unikitty llega a la conclusión de que todo el mundo sería mucho más feliz si pensara como ella, iy tal vez pueda lograrlo con la ayuda de la Dra. Fox! Unikitty copia sus ondas cerebrales en todos sus amigos y los Unikittyfica, para que todos puedan ser siempre positivos. Pero pronto, Unikitty se da cuenta de que puede haber un exceso de "buena princesa".

title: The Promise
description: Darwin has promised to play video games with Gumball, but there is a Banana Joe-shaped problem...

title: Overnight Stop
description: Percy feels anxious about spending a night away from home during an overnight delivery with Thomas and Nia.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Miss Juneteenth
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: Bad Penny
description: Ben is at the annual Big Bacon Pig Parade, but childhood friend Penny Heaven has met the family to ruin Ben's fun with her safety-obsessed self. While dodging Penny's overzealous safety precautions, Ben uncovers a plot by the Bug Brothers to steal helium from the parade balloons to rob banks with! Penny's badgering turns the heist into an accidental kidnapping so Ben must not only stop the robbery but save his least favorite safety monitor in the process.

title: Don
description: Rigby's estranged accountant brother comes back to help save the park from an audit. While everyone loves Don, Rigby wants nothing to do with him.

title: La Leyenda del Torbaclaun
description: Cuando los Corazoncitos creen que el mítico Torbaclaun ha llegado al Valle Puro Corazón, Mao Mao intenta demostrarles que no es real.

title: Royal Flush
description: When the other kids fear Harold has accidentally flushed himself down Chef's fancy new toilet, they travel into the sewer on a rescue mission. But will they find Harold before the mythical Alligator King traps them underground forever?

title: Super Screen Cleaners
description: Thomas pretends to be a hero to help ensure the movie screen Nia's delivering arrives clean and pristine.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: El Hada de los Gases
description: Después de perder su primer diente flojo por accidente y temer el no tener efectivo bajo la almohada, Leshawna intenta capturar al hada de los dientes. En vez de eso, captura al hada de los gases. Esto trae grandes consecuencias.

title: Gato de laboratorio
description: La Dra. Fox necesita Unikitty y Puppycorn como voluntarios para ser sus ratas de laboratorio, idigo, asistentes de investigación en un nuevo y audaz experimento que los lanzará al espacio! Pero a medida que la misión se vuelve más peligrosa, la Dra. Fox se ve obligada a elegir entre el avance científico de sus sueños y volver a ver a sus amigos.

title: Driller
description: Panthro is getting a little fed up with having to fix things around the Cats' Lair constantly, which is unfortunate because the ThunderCats are about to be attacked by an unstoppable drilling robot, and he's gonna break everything!

title: The Fan
description: Uncle Grandpa's number one fan gets more than he bargained for when Uncle Grandpa overstays his welcome.

title: #EnterNightSting
description: Karen is given a mission to prevent the apocalypse by DeathSting, a super-cool future version of herself.

title: Meet Panthro
description: Panthro may be the strongest cat on Third Earth, but one of his biggest strengths is that he can fix anything!  And the rest of the Thundercats break enough stuff to really put his skills to the test, but it's nothing a pro like Panthro can't handle.

title: Apple's Short
description: Apple wants to experience love.

title: Ghostfreaked Out
description: Ben's internal demons get externalized when Ghostfreak escapes from his watch and becomes a full fledged being on his own. The renegade alien then realizes he needs to meld with Ben's DNA in order to survive.

title: Blukic and Driba Go to Area 51
description: A mysterious Galvan arrives and demands Blukic and Driba to give back a super powerful weapon needed to stop a threat to Earth.

title: Hoots
description: A charismatic stranger in Finn's dream leads Cosmic Owl to shirk his duties.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin sets out to find a photo of Carrie for the cover of the school yearbook - but they end up reminiscing about all their past spooky shenanigans. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: El Silbon
description: Víctor arma un laberinto de maíz embrujado, pero los chicos del pueblo creen que es muy malo. Vic decide hacer que el laberinto sea más aterrador con la ayuda de El Silbón para asustar de verdad a los chicos, pero El Silbón tiene sus propios planes.

title: Baby Boi TP
description: Apple and Onion run out of toilet paper because Apple's been building a huge modern art sculpture with it. They're going to need more if Apple is to finish and Onion is to be able to resume his normal toilet activities.

title: The Finale
description: The Wattersons are surprised to discover that their past actions have consequences.

title: Sadie's Song
description: Steven helps Sadie put together an act for Beachapalooza.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Rivals
description: From Trigon to Terra to Darkseid, Robin counts down the worst of the worst: the greatest villains to ever challenge the Teen Titans!

title: Kelsey la autora
description: iCraig y Stacks ayudan a Kelsey a convertirse en una verdadera autora al convertir su historia en un libro!
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Zombozolandia
description: Ben, Gwen y Max vuelven a su parque de diversiones favorito... irenovado y rebautizado como AdrenaWORLD! Por desgracia, iel nuevo gerente es Zombozo, y su trío de secuaces! Zombozo planea hipnotizar a todos los visitantes del parque para formar un ejército criminal. Ben tiene que dejar de lado su deseo de subir a todos los juegos del parque y arreglar las cosas.

title: The Audition
description: The Bears audition to be the next mascot for their favorite cereal. They get so caught up in the process that their competitiveness gets the best of them.

title: Fiesta de cumpleanos
description: Master Frown, el habitante más pesimista del reino, se roba el deseo de cumpleaños de Puppycorn. Para recuperarlo, Unikitty y Puppycorn tendrán que aventurarse en la tierra más deprimente de la historia: iFrown Town! ¿Conseguirán recuperar el deseo de cumpleaños de manos de Frown antes de que su deseo (y todos los deseos) desaparezcan para siempre?

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Intergalactic Games
description: Super Hero High is facing off against Korugar Academy in the Intergalactic Games, but Lena Luthor takes advantage of the gathering of supers to enact her villainous plan.

title: Council of the Creek
description: The circle game wreaks havoc on the Creek, so Craig forms a council to restore order.

title: A Surprise for Pocoyo
description: Pocoyo's friends decide to give him a surprise party - simply to show him how much they love him.

title: The Birthday That Wasn't
description: Dibble misunderstands the Bears' intentions when they secretly make a plush toy Whiffle for her "Un-birthday." Thinking it's real and that the Bears love it more than they love her, she steals it and plans to leave it in the forest. She has second thoughts and returns her "rival" to her friends, only to learn that it's a gift to show their love for her.

title: Cat-Pocalypse
description: When Vic gets sick and is stuck in his room, he spies on Pineapple and becomes convinced that Pineapple is creating an army of zombie cats. Val agrees and the two become obsessed with stopping Pineapple before it's too late!

title: Back with a Vengeance
description: Ben's feeling cocky with the watch. He's unlocked its secret, and now can become any alien he wants, whenever he wants. That's the good news. The bad news is, after finding one another in the depths of space, Kevin 11 and Vilgax have teamed up and have returned to earth to destroy Ben and get the Omnitrix.

title: Birthday Blowout
description: Puppycorn's birthday wish is stolen by Master Frown, the biggest downer in the kingdom! To recover it, Unikitty and Puppycorn will have to venture into the most depressing land ever, Frown Town! Will they manage to recover the birthday wish from Frown before his wish (and all wishes) are wished away forever?

title: Conoce a Tu Mama
description: K.O. quiere sorprender a Carol con un regalo para el Día de la Madre, pero no sabe qué comprarle.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Ben 10,000
description: Ben gets sucked into the future by a grown up Gwen. His mission is to help the now all powerful and adult Ben 10,000 seemingly defeat the future versions of Dr. Animo and Vilgax. However, the real reason Ben has been brought to the future is to teach his adult self some humility and the fact he's lost touch with Max and has forgotten what's really important, family.

title: Guest Directed Shorts
description: A showcase of three Uncle Grandpa shorts presented in three unique animation styles.

title: Film Fest
description: It's opening night at the Unikingdom Film Festival! Everyone's excited to see what the friends made, particularly Richard, who considers himself the ultimate film expert and can't wait to blow everyone else's films out of the water with his own. But after playing the critic, will Rick's film be a masterpiece or a flop?

title: Captain Craboo
description: The Bears are reunited with their pet crab, Captain Craboo. But after an unfortunate run-in with Nom Nom, the Bears may lose their pet forever.

title: A Surprise for Mommy/Caillou Misses Sarah/T-Shirt Trouble/A Helping Hand
description: Dad gets a professional photo of Caillou and Rosie./Caillou's friend Sarah is going away on a trip for two whole weeks./Caillou's brand new T-shirt is ruined by grape juice./Caillou and Grandma, along with Rover the dog, spend a day at a retirement home.

title: Goat!
description: Prohyas becomes obsessed with riding an uncooperative goat to get over a mountain.

title: A Sumoful Mind
description: When Jeff realizes Sumo's new classes have been rubbing off on Sumo, he attempts to further foster this newfound intellectual Sumo! But will Clarence's lowbrow antics reverse Jeff's hard work?

title: Bird Call
description: Chanterelle has built a whistle that can reproduce the most beautiful sound of the forest: the one of the Nightingale. When the whistle disappears, Mush-Mush, Chep and Lilit soon discover that it has been stolen by a beetle. In order to finally hear what a real Nightingale sounds like, they'll have to get it back!

title: No Me Ataques, Amigo
description: Ben y Billy Billones, su archienemigo, se enfrentan en un duelo por la supremacía en Laser Town, el parque de simulación de armas láser. Pero cuando, sin darse cuenta, Billy desata una rebelión robótica, y los lásers pasan de tocar a desintegrar, isu juego infantil se convierte en una guerra sin cuartel! Los enemigos descubren que deben dejar de lado sus diferencias y unirse para poder salir con vida...iy salvar al resto del planeta!

title: Don't Let the Bass Drop
description: Ben and Gwen are excited to attend an Earth Day EDM concert in Portland until the show is hijacked by the sound-manipulating baddy Lord Decibel who uses sound as a weapon to trash the planet.

title: Exodus Part 2
description: Fleeing the destruction of their home planet Thundera, Lion-O and the ThunderCats land on the mysterious, dangerous, all-around awesome world of Third Earth! But their enemies, the Mutants of Plun-Darr have followed them and it turns out Third Earth already has a Mumm-Ra problem, can Lion-O learn the ropes of being a leader in time?

title: Developing Dilemna
description: Frankie lets Elliott get a pet, which doesn't go down well with their new neighbor.

title: Drawn to Making it Happen with Sidney Keys
description: Cartoon Network celebrates Black History Month with Sidney Keys III, a 15-year-old rising entrepreneur and the founder and CEO of "Books n Bros," an African American literature book club for male youth ages 7-13 years old. Focused on promoting literacy among young Black boys and introducing them to positive representation in literature, Keys' advocacy is paving the way for change by creating a place for boys to be mentored by their "Big Bros" and connect over a shared love for reading.

title: Home, Sweet Homesick
description: When the Girls go to Camp, Blossom has a hard time leaving her schoolwork at home.

title: Power-Noia
description: The girls have become paralyzed by their greatest fears. Who could be behind such an evil trick?

title: Snow Day
description: Steven and the Crystal Gems get a chance to catch up when they're all snowed in together.

title: Drawn to Community
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating awesome kids who are giving back and making a difference to those around them. CN is recognizing extraordinary girls who are channeling their interests into outreach as they are Drawn to… Community!

title: Know Your Mom
description: KO wants to surprise Carol with a gift for Mother's Day, but doesn't know what to get her.

title: Papel de Bano Bebecin
description: Manzana necesita conseguir la provisión del papel higiénico que usaría en toda su vida para terminar su escultura de arte moderno.

title: Lucas We Have a Problem/Egg-Scuse Me/Pokey Dokey
description: Lucas helps Bodhi fulfill her dream of touching a star./ Lucas finds an egg and decides to take care of it. But he learns that responsibility is hard./ When Avocado loses her beloved toy, Lucas and Findley are determined to cheer her up.
